<h1 style="text-transform:none;">Educator Resources for Cultural Competency</h1>
<p>These tools are designed to help schools work with parents  from diverse cultures to support the family&rsquo;s engagement in their child&rsquo;s  education.  Tools are provided to help  parents support their child&rsquo;s academic performance, become more informed  decision makers about their child&rsquo;s education, and improve home-school  communication and partnership.</p>

